{"tid":707994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聯俄] 美國參議員代表團或於7月訪問莫斯科","createTime":"2018-06-19T04:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:12:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12bf39b5b9accd7e6b1496b4ca861d9014c18046","tid":707994,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"美國參議員代表團或於7月訪問莫斯科<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1014536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1014536&d=FlOzQurTqKnjmcvyDim7wcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3e6a7f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1014536</a><br />\n<br />\n19.06.2018 11:12<br />\n美國一批參議員正籌備訪問俄羅斯，預計最快可於7月初成行。俄羅斯駐美國大使館證實，正為美國參議員代表團訪問莫斯科進行協調，希望對雙邊關係能產生積極影響。本身是共和黨籍的美國駐俄大使洪博培，過去多個月一直推動共和黨參議員代表團訪問莫斯科。俄羅斯聯邦委員會國際事務委員會主席科薩切夫透露，期望於7月初與美國參議員進行會談。<br />\n<br />\n美俄兩國關係因俄羅斯被指干預前年美國總統大選，一直處於冰點，近期兩國互動增加，俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫日前與美國國務卿蓬佩奧通電話，討論敘利亞危機、朝鮮半島和俄美近期政治接觸安排等事宜。"},{"pid":"2fc60e6d6953a00b87f298e6805eac346ced2216","tid":707994,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa81b95b78b60a7f3f0c1aa25950fe8565d6567","tid":707994,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"圍堵中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf662898bb321bbf96894fda80ef7f37f064042","tid":707994,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"TRUMP擺到明係玩「聯俄滅支」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fi